title: 为什么我用dynmap插件只能加载一小块地图啊?
author: linshi123123123
txt_content:
我按别人说的方法输入了/dynmap fullrender world


之后控制台提示这些.......
2:53:44 [INFO] Full render starting on world 'world'...
2:53:44 [INFO] [dynmap] Loading default resource pack
2:53:56 [INFO] Full render of map 'flat' of 'world' in progress - 100 tiles rendered (96.40 msec/tile, 43.29 msec per render)
2:53:56 [INFO] Full render of map 'flat' of 'world' completed - 104 tiles rendered (94.49 msec/map-tile, 41.97 msec per render)
2:54:16 [INFO] Unknown command. Type "help" for help.
2:54:25 [INFO] Full render of maps [surface,cave] of 'world' in progress - 100 tiles rendered each (138.12 msec/map-tile, 226.49 msec per render)
2:54:29 [INFO] Full render of maps [surface,cave] of 'world' completed - 115 tiles rendered each (130.75 msec/map-tile, 213.75 msec per render)
2:54:29 [INFO] Full render of 'world' finished.


怎么搞的啊?

replies.author: lichi2050
replies.txt_content: 这些很正常啊 你输入这个以后 需要等一会 他会显示更多的 不过你必须在游戏里面移动 让地图变大 dynmap 上面的地图才会变大
